dc_title_s: LiDAR-Derived Classified LAS for City of Superior (Douglas County), WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents LiDAR-derived classified LAS points for the City of Superior in Douglas County, Wisconsin in 2019. Point classification uses semi-automated techniques on the point cloud to assign the feature type associated with each point. LiDAR points can be classified into a number of categories including bare earth or ground, top of canopy, and water. The different classes are defined using numeric integer codes in the LAS files.
